HEADWORD: Liedertafel
<hw>Lie"der*ta`fel</hw> <pr>(l⟦emac⟧"d⟦etil⟧r*t⟦aum⟧`f'l)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G., lit., a song table.]</ety> <fld>(Mus.)</fld>
